        "牛角椒"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "椒"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "山顶、山头。",
      "examples": [
        "釋輿馬於山椒兮。——《汉书·外戚传》",
